comments: Lopez (MIL) establishes himself in McDaniels' (MIN) path and does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the pick.
Gobert (MIN) is moving forward slightly prior to marginal body contact occurring with Antetokounmpo (MIL) after Antetokounmpo retrieves the rebound.
McDaniels (MIN) jumps forward and initiates body contact that affects Antetokounmpo's (MIL) SQBR at the end of the drive.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) brings his left hand forward prior to marginal contact occurring with Towns' (MIN) right shoulder on the wing.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) legally contests Towns' (MIN) jump shot attempt.
Crowder's (MIL) hands come forward as he establishes himself in McDaniels' (MIN) path and marginal contact occurs with McDaniels' back as Crowder sets the pick.
Gobert (MIN) extends his right arm against Lillard's (MIL) front and initiates contact that affects Lillard's body trajectory as he elevates for the driving shot attempt.
McDaniels (MIN) initiates contact with Antetokounmpo's (MIL) side and extends into him as Antetokounmpo elevates to pursue the rebound.
Gobert (MIN) firms up in a screening position in Beasley's (MIL) path and marginal contact occurs as Beasley moves around the screen.
Crowder (MIL) grasps and then quickly releases Towns' (MIN) left arm as Towns moves to defend the drive.
Antetokounmpo's (MIL) momentum continues to carry him forward after he releases the pass and incidental contact occurs with Gobert (MIN) as Gobert begins to move to defend the shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) grasps and then quickly releases Towns' (MIN) jersey during the inbound.
Gobert (MIN) establishes himself in Beasley's (MIL) path following the hand-off and does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the pick.

Lopez (MIL) legally contests Edwards' (MIN) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released. Beasley (MIL) stops short of Edwards and would avoid him if he did not slightly extend his left leg backward to initiate the marginal contact after the release.
Anderson (MIN) and Lillard (MIL) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Conley (MIN) brings his right arm forward prior to marginal contact occurring with Lillard's (MIL) front at the end of the drive.
Crowder (MIL) avoids making contact with McDaniels (MIN), whom trips over Towns' (MIN) foot during the inbound.
Gobert (MIN) establishes himself in Beasley's (MIL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Beasley (MIL) and Lopez (MIL) each legally contest Edwards' (MIN) jump shot attempt.
Towns (MIN) attempts to commit a take foul on Lillard (MIL) and the contact is marginal.
